<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>레퍼브 초대</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0;">
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 500px; width: 100%;">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/30" alt="로고" style="width: 30px; height: 30px; margin-right: 10px;">
    </div>
    <h2 style="color: #282828; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      레퍼브 <span style="color: #1ABC9C;"><%= collection %></span> 컬렉션에 함께 하세요!
    </h2>
    <div style="width: 60px; border-top: 3px solid #FFD700; margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;"></div>
    <p style="color: #676967; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: left;">
      <b><%= owner %></b>님이 <b><%= name %></b>님을 <b><%= collection %></b> 컬렉션에 초대했습니다.<br>
      <b><%= collection %></b> 컬렉션에서 레퍼런스를 같이 공유해보세요.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="<%= link %>" style="color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #1ABC9C; border: none; padding: 0.8rem 2rem; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 15px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; transition: background-color 0.3s ease;">바로 이동하기</a>
    </p>
    <div style="color: #999999; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      * 계정이 없는 경우, 회원가입 후 컬렉션에 접근이 가능합니다.
    </div>
    <footer style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #999999; text-align: left;">
      📁 RefHub
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
